381
00:25:32,479 --> 00:25:34,760
But I'm only half day late.

382
00:25:35,119 --> 00:25:36,439
I'm really sorry.

383
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:39,000
How could you do that?

384
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,479
