to someone else

387
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,640
as you wish?

388
00:25:46,359 --> 00:25:49,359
Miss Du,

389
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:51,439
if I tell you the truth

390
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:52,839
about this house,

391
00:25:53,359 --> 00:25:55,199
