393
00:25:58,199 --> 00:25:59,280
Who on earth

394
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,199
bought my house?

395
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:05,719
Mr. Lei, Du Xiaosu from Design Team
wants to see you.

396
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,719
Tell her that I don't want to see her.

397
