466
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,280
to achieve the goal.

467
00:29:22,119 --> 00:29:23,319
I will be back.

468
00:29:29,719 --> 00:29:32,680
Mr. Xie, I've learned so much

469
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,520
by having meal and talking with you.

470
00:29:36,479 --> 00:29:37,640
